eaching influences behind it.\r\n\r\nFirst of all, AI contribute to enhance the efficiency of workers and provides them with more adequate rest time. Depending upon a rough estimate of the relevant department,nearly 87% of the respondents hold the same view.In addition, AI enables beginners to quickly enter the industry and also facilitates their acquisition of basic knowledge in other fields. AS is stated by Anthropic, a well-known expert in the field of AI,"You can never overlook the function of AI technology on the rapid development of the world."\r\n\r\nFrom what has been discussed, we may safely draw the conclusion that great significance should be attached to AI. Everyone should cultivate a better awareness of it and take practical actions.\n上述内容是我写的一篇英语作文，要求在120-180词之间，请根据我的作文结构，提炼出一套任何议论文都可以使用的通用模板出来。','\r',char(13)),'\n',char(10)),1781196737,1781196737627,'legacy');
