n the full breadth of human reasoning and code. The harness did not make Claude smart. Claude was already smart. The harness gave Claude hands, eyes, and a workspace.\r\012README.md:1<truncated omitted_approx_tokens="3698" />tries acceptEdits mode simulation (`permissions.ts:620-656`, if acceptEdits allows → auto-approve), then checks the safe tool whitelist (`permissions.ts:658-686`), and finally calls the classifier. If the classifier rejects too many times in a row → falls back to manual approval.\r\012s03_permission\README.en.md:220:A sub-Agent''s (forked via AgentTool) `permissionMode` is set to `''bubble''` (`forkSubagent.ts:50`). This means permission dialogs **bubble up to the parent Agent''s terminal**, rather than being silently denied in the sub-Agent. The Bash classifier continues running during this process — displaying the permission dialog while judging in the background whether auto-approval is possible.\r\012s03_permission\README.en.md:226:- isDestructive → omitted (teaching version has no UI layer, and it doesn''t participate in permission decisions in CC either)\r\012docs\zh\s10-team-protocols.md:13:**关机**: 直接杀线程会留下写了一半的文件和过期的 config.json。需要握手 -- 领导请求, 队友批准 (收尾退出) 或拒绝 (继续干)。\r\012s03_permission\images\permission-pipeline.svg:42:  <text x="657" y="116" fill="#64748b" font-size="8" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">允许 / 拒绝</text>\r\012s03_permission\images\permission-pipeline.svg:57:  <text x="591" y="184" fill="#166534" font-size="11" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">允许 (allow)</text>\r\012s03_permission\images\permission-pipeline.svg:58:  <text x="591" y="200" fill="#166534" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle">规则未命中，或用户允许</text>\r\012s03_permission\images\permission-pipeline.svg:60:  <text x="371" y="248" fill="#64748b" font-size="10" text-anchor="middle">规则优先：闸门 1 硬拒绝 → 闸门 2 规则匹配 → 命中则用户审批，未命中默认允许</text>\r\012s03_permission\images\permission-overview.ja.svg:57:  <text x="482" y="100" fill="#991b1b" font-size="11" font-weight="700" text-