mit to preserve the existing selection on update, or pass null to clear it. Cron automations only."},"model":{"type":"string","description":"Model to use for cron automations."},"reasoningEffort":{"type":"string","description":"Reasoning effort to use for cron automations. One of none, minimal, low, medium, high, or xhigh."},"targetThreadId":{"type":"string","description":"Target thread id for heartbeat automations. Prefer destination=thread when the automation should attach to the current local thread."},"status":{"type":"string","description":"One of ACTIVE or PAUSED."}},"additionalProperties":false}',0,NULL);
